postcontent:
Like new, bought earlier this year.  Gun has been shot maybe 20 times, it's ideal for anyone into big bore revolvers and great for hunting!  Comes with scope mount and two sets (medium and high) of fiber optic front sights that are interchangeable between red and green, plus the standard black ramp front sight too.

These are really nice guns, without question they're nicer than any Ruger single action.  From the factory it has a hand lapped barrel, recessed cylinders (it's a 5 shot), a free spinning cylinder, a locking base pin, drilled and tapped for scope use and has a good trigger on it too.
